<span id="freeTextContainer14324130964889596180">Uhm.. this was boring? <br/><br/>And maybe I&apos;m uncultured or whatever but my god all of those Shakespeare quotes annoyed the hell out of me. <br/>I didn&apos;t care for any of the characters, I didn&apos;t care for the plot and I didn&apos;t care who the murderer was (and if we&apos;re being honest, there wasn&apos;t even really a mystery here. I don&apos;t know if some stuff was supposed to be shocking or not, but it definitely was not thrilling) <br/><br/>I was bored out of my mind.<br/><br/><br/><br/>(And what&apos;s with those weird comments Oliver made about his sister</span>
